<section class="section" id="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-title">
  <h2 id="problem-title">The Problem</h2>
  <p>Filament-only math misses true print cost. Real prints depend on more than grams used.</p>
  <div class="section-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Filament Alone Is Incomplete</h3>
      <p>Many makers only price by grams used, which underestimates final cost.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Electricity Is Printer-Specific</h3>
      <p>Power draw varies by machine and print length, and can materially change total cost.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Multiple Materials Change Totals</h3>
      <p>Mixed-material prints need more than one filament input to stay accurate.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Advanced Pricing Needs Extra Controls</h3>
      <p>Labour, failure risk, markup, and setup fees matter when you need business pricing.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="solution" aria-labelledby="solution-title">
  <h2 id="solution-title">The Solution</h2>
  <p>Start with accurate print cost in Free, then move to Premium when you need faster batch workflows, business pricing controls, exports, and stock tracking.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Multi-material filament costing</li>
    <li>Printer-specific electricity costing</li>
    <li>Single-print G-code import</li>
    <li>Manual batch costing</li>
    <li>History and single-job export</li>
    <li>Premium pricing controls for labour, failure risk, markup, setup fees, and rounding rules</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="section" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-title">
  <h2 id="features-title">Key Features</h2>
  <div class="section-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Core Calculator</h3>
      <p>Core print costing and electricity costing are included in Free and Premium.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Multi-Material Costing</h3>
      <p>Included in Free and Premium. Free supports saved materials plus up to 1 Unsaved Material per calculation.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Saved Materials</h3>
      <p>Free includes up to 5 saved materials. Premium removes the cap.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Printer Profiles</h3>
      <p>Free includes up to 2 printer profiles. Premium includes unlimited printer profiles.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>History</h3>
      <p>Free includes up to 7 history entries with real access to that list. Premium includes unlimited history.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Single-Print G-code Import</h3>
      <p>Included in Free and Premium for supported files.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Batch Costing</h3>
      <p>Free includes manual batch costing for up to 3 items per batch. Premium adds unlimited batch costing and batch G-code import.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Exports and Stock Tracking</h3>
      <p>Single-job export is included in Free and Premium. Premium adds bulk/full history export, batch quote export, and remaining filament / stock tracking.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

